  "title": "Sales Engineer (Mechanical)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and manage projects and sales opportunities and develop new accounts to drive revenue growth with potential &amp; existing customer.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and deliver technical presentations explaining product or services to existing and prospective customers.</li>\n  <li>Understand customers’ needs and competitors in order to develop strategy to win sales.</li>\n  <li>Liaise and work closely with sales support staff/application engineer.</li>\n  <li>Provide sales and first-level technical support to all customers’ enquiries, deliveries and issues or feedback.</li>\n  <li>Product selection and generate quotations based on RFQ.</li>\n  <li>Project sales management and submission of Sales Report.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Engineering (Mechanical) or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Min 1 years of working experience in the related field is required.</li>\n  <li>Possess Class 3 Driving License.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online <strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong>or call <strong>+(65) 6513 5697</strong> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd. </strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
